did you start your function definition with def? 
does function name have only characters and _ characters? 
did you put ( right after the function name? 
did you put ) and a : after the arguments? 
did you indent all lines of code you want in the function four spaces? 
did you 'end' your function by going back to writing with no indent? 

to run ("use" or "call") a function:
did you call/use/run this function by typing the name? 
did you put ( after the name to run it? 
did you end the values you want into the () separated my commas? 
did you end function call with )? 

